These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, blue, chestnut, light-blue
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, time-travel, action, thriller
House: art-deco, colonial, ranch-style, tower
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, skateboarding, volleyball, swimming
 1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
 2. the person who likes blue is the person watching thriller movies##1
 3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
 5. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
 7. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
 8. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
 9. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far left##1
10. the ranch-style house is on the right of the colonial house##1
11. the colonial house is on the left of the person who likes red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |   4   |
| Color    | chestnut   | blue       | red | light-blue   |
| Movie-Genre        | time-travel    | thriller  | action      | scientific |
| House         | tower      | colonial | ranch-style         | art-deco   |
| Sport   | skiing | skateboarding       | volleyball        | swimming   |

