.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, d&b, disco, electronic
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, january, november, july
House: gothic-revival, victorian, colonial, craftsman
There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, mauve, turquise, azure
1. the colonial house is on the left of the victorian house##1
2. the fan of d&b is the person who's birthday is in april##1
3. the person who likes turquise is the fan of disco##1
4. the fan of techno is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person who likes yellow##2
5. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
6. the craftsman house is the person who likes azure##1
7. the gothic-revival house is on the far right##1
8. the person who likes yellow is on the far left or far right##3
9. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |       3        |      4       |
| Music-Genre           | d&b | techno | electronic | disco |
| Birthday   | april  | november | january         | july      |
| House         | colonial      | victorian    | craftsman         | gothic-revival   |
| Color     | yellow         | mauve    | azure          | turquise         |

