.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, may, october, april
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, 7up, cola, juice
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, reading, gardening, fishing
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, ivory, blood-red, apricot
 1. the person drinking cola is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who likes blood-red##3
 4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
 5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 6. the person who likes ivory is on the left or right of the person who likes apricot##3
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
 8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person who likes blood-red and the person drinking 7up##2
 9. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
10. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |     4      |
| Birthday          | may | april  | december | october      |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate       | juice    | 7up      | cola      |
| Hobby           | fishing     | rock-climbing     | reading         | gardening   |
| Color         | blood-red | blue | ivory     | apricot |

