6. the person who likes red is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
8. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person eating lime and the person who likes emerald##2
9. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person eating grapefruit##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4       |
| Birthday           | july     | april | june | november |
