The people have 4 different jobs:  musician, freelancer, lawyer, accountant
 1. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the musician##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who likes green##1
 3. the accountant is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who likes lilac is on the left or right of the person who likes white##3
 5. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the accountant##1
 7. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the freelancer##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who likes white##1
 9. the accountant is the person who growsazalea##1
10. the musician is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy##3
11. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who likes ivory##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3       |     4     |
| Color         | ivory      | white | lilac       | green   |
| Birthday   | may     | december | october | august |
| Flower   | balloon-flower    | poppy     | begonia        | azalea       |
| Job     | lawyer | freelancer   | musician   | accountant       |

