.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-20::.
City: colone, marseilles, berlin, liverpool
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, chess, domino, poker
House: farmhouse, colonial, art-deco, cape-cod
4 different pets are kept: cat, rat, guinea-pig, ferret
 1. the person traveling to colone is on the far right##1
 2. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 3. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 4. the person playing chess is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the owner of the rat##2
 5. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the person traveling to berlin##3
 6. the farmhouse house is between the person playing chess and the owner of the cat##2
 7. the art-deco house is the person playing poker##1
 8. the art-deco house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
 9. the person traveling to berlin is the person playing chess##1
10. the farmhouse house is the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |     4     |
| City          | marseilles | liverpool   | berlin   | colone |
| Game           | mah-jongg   | domino     | chess   | poker |
| House   | colonial    | farmhouse    | cape-cod   | art-deco   |
| Pet         | cat    | rat | ferret | guinea-pig    |

 